          <documentation>Although this layer has no ArchiMate equivalent, many of its concepts (attribute profiles, metrics, risk analysis, control objectives &amp; layering) have already been discussed in the context of: The Security Overlay of the Motivation Metamodel.&#xD;
This section examines how the remaining security concepts and artefacts can be modelled. It will also consider how the Conceptual layer can be inserted between the Contextual and Logical layers.</documentation>
        </element>
